def print_mean_std(data, sample_name):
    print(f'  {sample_name} ')
    print()
    print(np.mean(data))
    print()
    print(f'   {sample_name} ')
    print()
    print(np.std(data))
    print()

def print_metrics(y_true, y_pred, y_proba, model):
    print('   ' + model)
    print()
    print('\tAccuracy: {:.2f}'.format(accuracy_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tPrecision: {:.2f}'.format(precision_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tRecall: {:.2f}'.format(recall_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tF1_score: {:.2f}'.format(f1_score(y_true, y_pred)))
    print('\tROC_AUC: {:.2f}'.format(roc_auc_score(y_true, y_proba)))
    print()
print_metrics(y_test, predictions_lr, probabilities_lr, '" "')
print_metrics(y_test, predictions_rf, probabilities_rf, '" "')
